These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, entrepreneur, lawyer
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
2. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
3. the person driving the ship is between the entrepreneur and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | entrepreneur | firefighter   | lawyer |
| Transport   | taxi | ship | scooter        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, coffee
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, mouse
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
3. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate   | juice   |
| Pet        | bird | mouse | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: onion, grapes, watermelon
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, airplane
1. the person eating onion is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person eating onion and the person driving the helicopter##7
3. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
4. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | grapes | watermelon | onion |
| Transport   | helicopter       | airplane     | boat         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, social-worker, electrician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, crime
1. the electrician is not to the right of the social-worker##8
2. the electrician is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | electrician | social-worker |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | superhero | animation    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, superhero, disaster
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, rat
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
4. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | disaster | action |
| Pet           | guinea-pig    | rat      | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
