2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
3. the firefighter is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
4. the journalist is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | journalist | dressmaker | firefighter |
| Pet   | rabbit        | mouse   | lizard     |

