2. the person drinking water is not to the left of the mechanic##8
3. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the mechanic##8
4. the mechanic is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water | coffee |
| Job        | mechanic      | social-worker    | software-developer |

