.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, peas, papaya
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, spy
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
2. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | papaya | cucumber  | peas |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | satire | spy   |

