.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, water-polo
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
5. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | milk | iced-tea        | 7up    |
| Sport      | basketball  | water-polo | lacrosse |

