.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, water
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, rock-climbing
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person drinking tea##7
3. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate     | water | tea   |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | fishing | cooking |

