1. the fan of indie is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of indie is between the fan of classical and the fan of trance##2
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the fan of classical is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | indie      | classical |
| Sport         | climbing | baseball | golf     |

