2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | asparagus | peas | lettuce    |
| Pet    | hamster   | pony      | hedgehog |

