2. the italian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
3. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | dancing | singing | reading |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican    | italian    |

 